the gods, and he was punished,

00:12:15.620 --> 00:12:18.550 align:middle line:84%
or it was punished and
stripped of his title,

00:12:18.550 --> 00:12:21.940 align:middle line:90%
and he became the trickster.

00:12:21.940 --> 00:12:26.320 align:middle line:84%
And it is said that
this entity taught--

00:12:26.320 --> 00:12:29.870 align:middle line:84%
before he became the trickster,
he taught the language.

00:12:29.870 --> 00:12:32.240 align:middle line:90%
He taught Lakota.

00:12:32.240 --> 00:12:35.240 align:middle line:84%
This entity named
things in the universe.

00:12:35.240 --> 00:12:38.600 align:middle line:84%
And so that's where our
language comes from.

00:12:38.600 --> 00:12:41.650 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: So is it fair to say,
