it in that context,

00:12:58.060 --> 00:12:59.920 align:middle line:90%
but he's certainly otherworldly.

00:12:59.920 --> 00:13:00.150 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Yeah.

00:13:00.150 --> 00:13:02.150 align:middle line:84%
>> IRON EYES: And you
could even say that this--

00:13:02.150 --> 00:13:06.707 align:middle line:84%
