banished here, this--

00:13:06.707 --> 00:13:07.540 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: To Earth.

00:13:07.540 --> 00:13:09.900 align:middle line:84%
>> IRON EYES: --Gaia, mama
Gaia [SPEAKING LAKOTA].

00:13:09.900 --> 00:13:11.880 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: Oh, was
that a punishment?

00:13:11.880 --> 00:13:13.890 align:middle line:84%
>> IRON EYES: Yeah,
it was a punishment.

