you know what I'm saying.

00:13:23.260 --> 00:13:23.500 align:middle line:90%
So--

00:13:23.500 --> 00:13:25.360 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: And are these real
forces still present today?

00:13:25.360 --> 00:13:26.700 align:middle line:90%
>> IRON EYES: Absolutely.

00:13:26.700 --> 00:13:28.980 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: Are they present
