When my wife moved us to the
Standing Rock Reservation--

00:21:32.400 --> 00:21:34.622 align:middle line:84%
well, that's where I
grew up until I was 19,

00:21:34.622 --> 00:21:36.330 align:middle line:84%
I was raised on the
Standing Rock Nation.

00:21:36.330 --> 00:21:39.380 align:middle line:90%
And I had gone off to school.

00:21:39.380 --> 00:21:43.150 align:middle line:84%
I'd given my time and energy
to this Western academic

00:21:43.150 --> 00:21:45.680 align:middle line:84%
experience, and I learned
great things there.

00:21:45.680 --> 00:21:47.245 align:middle line:90%
I learned good things there.

00:21:47.245 --> 00:21:51.230 align:middle line:84%
I studied a bit of political
philosophy, and I loved it.

00:21:51.230 --> 00:21:53.780 align:middle line:84%
I liked it, and I loved
it, and it activated me.

00:21:53.780 --> 00:21:54.580 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Yeah.

00:21:54.580 --> 00:21:56.090 align:middle line:84%
You had the intellectual
challenge of this whole--

00:21:56.090 --> 00:21:56.350 align:middle line:90%
>> IRON EYES: Yeah.

00:21:56.350 --> 00:21:57.040 align:middle line:90%
It was--

00:21:57.040 --> 00:21:57.830 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: --landscape.

00:21:57.830 --> 00:21:58.580 align:middle line:90%
Yeah.

00:21:58.580 --> 00:21:59.780 align:middle line:90%
>> IRON EYES: I appreciate it.

00:21:59.780 --> 00:22:00.580 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Yeah.

00:22:00.580 --> 00:22:04.150 align:middle line:84%
>> IRON EYES: And
then I ended up back--

00:22:04.150 --> 00:22:06.980 align:middle line:84%
we ended up back proximate
to the reservation,

00:22:06.980 --> 00:22:10.190 align:middle line:84%
and my wife took a job on the
Standing Rock Reservation.

00:22:10.190 --> 00:22:11.090 align:middle line:90%
So I moved back.

00:22:11.090 --> 00:22:12.140 align:middle line:90%
We all moved back.

00:22:12.140 --> 00:22:14.980 align:middle line:84%
And the gentleman who was
giving me a tour of the house,

00:22:14.980 --> 00:22:16.910 align:middle line:90%
he's a speaker.

00:22:16.910 --> 00:22:17.960 align:middle line:90%
He's Lakota.

00:22:17.960 --> 00:22:21.860 align:middle line:84%
His name is Councilman
Richard-- he's a Councilman now,

00:22:21.860 --> 00:22:23.090 align:middle line:90%
Richard Long Feather.

00:22:23.090 --> 00:22:26.004 align:middle line:84%
But he comes up to me and
he says, [SPEAKING LAKOTA].

00:22:26.004 --> 00:22:31.150 align:middle line:90%


00:22:31.150 --> 00:22:32.060 align:middle line:90%
I'm doing all right.

00:22:32.060 --> 00:22:35.440 align:middle line:84%
He's just asking
me how I'm doing.

00:22:35.440 --> 00:22:39.450 align:middle line:84%
He was raised by old people, so
he thinks that I'm a speaker.

00:22:39.450 --> 00:22:43.800 align:middle line:84%
And he just starts going off
in Lakota for the full tour.

00:22:43.800 --> 00:22:48.240 align:middle line:84%
And at some point, he looked
at me and he goes, [LAKOTA],

00:22:48.240 --> 00:22:49.980 align:middle line:84%
do you understand
what I'm saying?

00:22:49.980 --> 00:22:50.847 align:middle line:90%
And I--

00:22:50.847 --> 00:22:51.701 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: A little bit.

00:22:51.701 --> 00:22:54.159 align:middle line:84%
>> IRON EYES: [LAKOTA], a little
bit, you know what I mean?

00:22:54.159 --> 00:22:57.170 align:middle line:84%
I can-- But after he spoke
the language to me for about--

00:22:57.170 --> 00:23:01.160 align:middle line:84%
only about five minutes, I go
out to my car, and I'm in tears,

00:23:01.160 --> 00:23:02.105 align:middle line:90%
and I can feel--

00:23:02.105 --> 00:23:03.270 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Yeah, activated.

00:23:03.270 --> 00:23:06.200 align:middle line:84%
>> IRON EYES: I can feel
something being secreted,

00:23:06.200 --> 00:23:08.042 align:middle line:90%
either on my skull or spine,

00:23:08.042 --> 00:23:09.000 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Interesting.

00:23:09.000 --> 00:23:10.370 align:middle line:90%
>> IRON EYES: --you might say.

00:23:10.370 --> 00:23:15.000 align:middle line:84%
And it's-- I don't
know what the word is.

00:23:15.000 --> 00:23:16.880 align:middle line:90%
It's subliming me.

00:23:16.880 --> 00:23:18.450 align:middle line:90%
It's just taking over me.

00:23:18.450 --> 00:23:21.025 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: So you're going
into almost a euphoric opening,

00:23:21.025 --> 00:23:21.330 align:middle line:90%
state.

00:23:21.330 --> 00:23:22.747 align:middle line:84%
>> IRON EYES:
There's a vibration.

00:23:22.747 --> 00:23:26.430 align:middle line:84%
I just feel one of the best
I've ever felt in my life.

00:23:26.430 --> 00:23:27.230 align:middle line:90%
Just from--

00:23:27.230 --> 00:23:28.813 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: Just
hearing that language.

00:23:28.813 --> 00:23:29.630 align:middle line:90%
>> IRON EYES: Yes.

00:23:29.630 --> 00:23:30.800 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Beautiful.

00:23:30.800 --> 00:23:32.230 align:middle line:84%
Yeah, no, I just
had to ask you--

00:23:32.230 --> 00:23:34.230 align:middle line:84%
I hadn't planned on going
down that rabbit hole,

00:23:34.230 --> 00:23:36.980 align:middle line:84%
but it seems like it's
so important in terms

00:23:36.980 --> 00:23:40.760 align:middle line:84%
of the preservation of not
just your tradition, but higher

00:23:40.760 --> 00:23:44.090 align:middle line:84%
frequencies from here
or elsewhere that really

00:23:44.090 --> 00:23:45.985 align:middle line:90%
can't afford to be obliterated.

00:23:45.985 --> 00:23:48.520 align:middle line:84%
You need to keep
those frequencies.

00:23:48.520 --> 00:23:49.320 align:middle line:90%
OK.

00:23:49.320 --> 00:23:50.862 align:middle line:84%
So I'm going to go
back for a second.

00:23:50.862 --> 00:23:54.920 align:middle line:84%
You said the trickster
got the people who

00:23:54.920 --> 00:23:58.220 align:middle line:84%
were living inside the
earth, and many stories

00:23:58.220 --> 00:24:00.020 align:middle line:90%
are coming up now.

00:24:00.020 --> 00:24:01.820 align:middle line:84%
The Radu Cinamar
books are all about

00:24:01.820 --> 00:24:04.530 align:middle line:84%
the cultures living inside
the Earth, the tunneling down,

00:24:04.530 --> 00:24:07.070 align:middle line:84%
the stuff going on, the
holographic chambers

00:24:07.070 --> 00:24:09.330 align:middle line:84%
inside the earth, a
lot of stuff in those.

00:24:09.330 --> 00:24:12.390 align:middle line:84%
And another book by Sarah
Breskman, who I interviewed--

00:24:12.390 --> 00:24:13.440 align:middle line:90%
she does regressions.

00:24:13.440 --> 00:24:15.690 align:middle line:84%
I'll bring something up on
that later, a little later.

00:24:15.690 --> 00:24:20.180 align:middle line:84%
But people talking about
the Tuatha Dé Danann

00:24:20.180 --> 00:24:22.340 align:middle line:84%
and some of the other
realms of beings

00:24:22.340 --> 00:24:23.960 align:middle line:84%
living on the
inside of the earth

00:24:23.960 --> 00:24:25.430 align:middle line:90%
and then coming to the surface.

00:24:25.430 --> 00:24:27.680 align:middle line:84%
And you're saying that your
people were on the inside,

00:24:27.680 --> 00:24:30.630 align:middle line:84%
and they were tricked into
coming onto the surface.

00:24:30.630 --> 00:24:34.010 align:middle line:84%
And it was kind of, as I
recall, summertime conditions.

00:24:34.010 --> 00:24:35.420 align:middle line:90%
Like, this isn't so bad, until--

00:24:35.420 --> 00:24:36.220 align:middle line:90%
>> IRON EYES: Yes.

00:24:36.220 --> 00:24:37.640 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: --winter came.

00:24:37.640 --> 00:24:41.840 align:middle line:84%
>> IRON EYES: That trickster
was living here with two other--

00:24:41.840 --> 00:24:43.998 align:middle line:84%
it's called
double-faced woman and--

00:24:43.998 --> 00:24:46.290 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: Well, that doesn't
sound good to begin with.

00:24:46.290 --> 00:24:48.266 align:middle line:90%
>> IRON EYES: [LAKOTA].

00:24:48.266 --> 00:24:52.560 align:middle line:84%
These are figures
in our worldview.

00:24:52.560 --> 00:24:59.070 align:middle line:84%
And so the trickster went in--
sent a wolf laden with a pack.

00:24:59.070 --> 00:25:01.820 align:middle line:84%
And in that pack are
all of the things that

00:25:01.820 --> 00:25:04.970 align:middle line:84%
are going to appeal to
the two-legged being,

00:25:04.970 --> 00:25:07.712 align:middle line:84%
or the beings that
are underneath there.

00:25:07.712 --> 00:25:10.160 align:middle line:90%
What became us, what was us.

00:25:10.160 --> 00:25:15.950 align:middle line:84%
And first opens up the most
beautiful song from one

00:25:15.950 --> 00:25:19.820 align:middle line:84%
of maybe a meadowlark or
a songbird from the earth.

00:25:19.820 --> 00:25:24.650 align:middle line:84%
And then shows them the most
beautiful blooming flower

00:25:24.650 --> 00:25:27.900 align:middle line:84%
and lets them smell it,
shows them a smoked hide,

00:25:27.900 --> 00:25:33.392 align:middle line:84%
smell this smoked hide,
hear these beautiful songs.

00:25:33.392 --> 00:25:34.350 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Come hither.

00:25:34.350 --> 00:25:37.660 align:middle line:84%
>> IRON EYES: Everything
that appeals to the senses.

00:25:37.660 --> 00:25:40.760 align:middle line:84%
Touch these soft
furs and soft hides.

00:25:40.760 --> 00:25:43.720 align:middle line:10%
And then the final
thing was now,

00:25:43.720 --> 00:25:47.140 align:middle line:10%
taste this meat,
this Buffalo meat.

00:25:47.140 --> 00:25:48.780 align:middle line:10%
And when we tasted the--

00:25:48.780 --> 00:25:50.780 align:middle line:10%
see, we weren't supposed
to come to the surface.

00:25:50.780 --> 00:25:53.280 align:middle line:84%
But when we tasted the Buffalo
meat, then we're like, OK.

00:25:53.280 --> 00:25:54.080 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: I'm in.

00:25:54.080 --> 00:25:55.880 align:middle line:84%
>> IRON EYES: I'm
going to disobey God.

00:25:55.880 --> 00:25:56.300 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Yeah.

00:25:56.300 --> 00:25:57.925 align:middle line:84%
>> IRON EYES: I'm
going to disobey God,

00:25:57.925 --> 00:26:00.620 align:middle line:84%
and we're going to the
surface with this--

00:26:00.620 --> 00:26:03.010 align:middle line:90%
this entity here.

00:26:03.010 --> 00:26:07.240 align:middle line:84%
Every culture has a story
like that where they

00:26:07.240 --> 00:26:09.920 align:middle line:90%
emerge into this other world.

00:26:09.920 --> 00:26:12.287 align:middle line:90%
And it's also--

00:26:12.287 --> 00:26:14.120 align:middle line:84%
I know from some of the
Eastern traditions--

00:26:14.120 --> 00:26:15.460 align:middle line:90%
I don't know what--

00:26:15.460 --> 00:26:19.420 align:middle line:84%
I read some of the Bhagavad
Gita, maybe the song of god

00:26:19.420 --> 00:26:21.470 align:middle line:84%
and Krishna's counsel
in the time of war.

00:26:21.470 --> 00:26:25.660 align:middle line:84%
I'm interested in a lot of
other seekers and seekers

00:26:25.660 --> 00:26:27.700 align:middle line:90%
in different cultures.

00:26:27.700 --> 00:26:32.840 align:middle line:84%
But they talk about the nine
gates to the kingdom of heaven,

00:26:32.840 --> 00:26:35.120 align:middle line:84%
I think it is, or
the city of heaven

00:26:35.120 --> 00:26:38.260 align:middle line:84%
being the two eyes, the
nostrils, the mouth, the ears,

00:26:38.260 --> 00:26:39.060 align:middle line:90%
the--

00:26:39.060 --> 00:26:39.977 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: The senses?

00:26:39.977 --> 00:26:44.120 align:middle line:84%
>> IRON EYES: --sex organ, the
digestive organ, and the senses.

00:26:44.120 --> 00:26:45.450 align:middle line:90%
It's the same thing.

00:26:45.450 --> 00:26:46.250 align:middle line:90%
And--

00:26:46.250 --> 00:26:47.050 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Yes.

00:26:47.050 --> 00:26:50.610 align:middle line:84%
>> IRON EYES: --is we have
this high righteous knowledge,

00:26:50.610 --> 00:26:54.330 align:middle line:84%
this ancient knowledge, but it's
been completely downplayed--

00:26:54.330 --> 00:26:58.170 align:middle line:84%
they tell a story like
we're some primitive people.

00:26:58.170 --> 00:26:59.578 align:middle line:90%
We're Stone Age people.

00:26:59.578 --> 00:27:01.620 align:middle line:84%
I mean, yeah, we were
alive during the Stone Age,

00:27:01.620 --> 00:27:04.550 align:middle line:84%
but we just had-- we
had different goals.

00:27:04.550 --> 00:27:08.790 align:middle line:84%
And so we emerged
onto the earth.

00:27:08.790 --> 00:27:10.550 align:middle line:90%
We disobeyed God.

00:27:10.550 --> 00:27:16.860 align:middle line:84%
And the trickster looked
at us, summertime went by.

00:27:16.860 --> 00:27:20.070 align:middle line:84%
It began to get so cold
that we couldn't live.

00:27:20.070 --> 00:27:21.517 align:middle line:90%
And we went-- we ran back--

00:27:21.517 --> 00:27:21.930 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: No birds.

00:27:21.930 --> 00:27:22.730 align:middle line:90%
Yeah.

00:27:22.730 --> 00:27:25.290 align:middle line:84%
>> IRON EYES: We ran back to
the cave in the Black Hills.

00:27:25.290 --> 00:27:25.770 align:middle line:90%
It's still there.

00:27:25.770 --> 00:27:27.720 align:middle line:84%
It's the National Park,
Wind Cave National Park.

00:27:27.720 --> 00:27:29.178 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: Yes,
I've read about it.

00:27:29.178 --> 00:27:33.160 align:middle line:84%
>> IRON EYES: And we said,
God, we made a mistake.

00:27:33.160 --> 00:27:33.960 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Too bad.

00:27:33.960 --> 00:27:34.877 align:middle line:90%
>> IRON EYES: Too bad.

00:27:34.877 --> 00:27:36.937 align:middle line:84%
You're there now, and
you have to endure.

00:27:36.937 --> 00:27:38.770 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: Kind of like
everybody else here.

00:27:38.770 --> 00:27:39.570 align:middle line:90%
>> IRON EYES: Yes.

00:27:39.570 --> 00:27:41.028 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: You guys
weren't exempt.

00:27:41.028 --> 00:27:41.980 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHTER]

00:27:41.980 --> 00:27:43.490 align:middle line:90%
Here we all are.

00:27:43.490 --> 00:27:48.710 align:middle line:84%
But the good thing is,
with the Native Americans,

00:27:48.710 --> 00:27:51.580 align:middle line:84%
the people here,
there was-- there

00:27:51.580 --> 00:27:53.680 align:middle line:84%
continued to be
a connection with

00:27:53.680 --> 00:27:57.760 align:middle line:84%
and a reverence for Mother
Earth and nature itself,

00:27:57.760 --> 00:28:01.240 align:middle line:84%
which was certainly lost over
the last couple of centuries

00:28:01.240 --> 00:28:02.720 align:middle line:90%
of industrialization.

00:28:02.720 --> 00:28:06.950 align:middle line:84%
And this seems to me, it doesn't
even matter who I'm talking to,

00:28:06.950 --> 00:28:09.590 align:middle line:84%
who I'm interviewing,
what book I'm reading.

00:28:09.590 --> 00:28:15.040 align:middle line:84%
Our path to truth is to get
rid of the trickster, which

00:28:15.040 --> 00:28:18.880 align:middle line:84%
is everything we're being
led to believe right, back

00:28:18.880 --> 00:28:22.230 align:middle line:84%
to nature and our essential
selves and our hearts, right?

00:28:22.230 --> 00:28:23.030 align:middle line:90%
>> IRON EYES: Yes.

00:28:23.030 --> 00:28:26.140 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: And so this is where
the Native Americans have a big

00:28:26.140 --> 00:28:28.940 align:middle line:84%
jump on the rest
of us around here.

00:28:28.940 --> 00:28:33.500 align:middle line:84%
>> IRON EYES: We all have
senses, and we have--

00:28:33.500 --> 00:28:35.910 align:middle line:90%
my reason, consciousness.

00:28:35.910 --> 00:28:38.730 align:middle line:84%
We have different words
for those concepts.

00:28:38.730 --> 00:28:42.210 align:middle line:84%
And sometimes I don't even know
if they translate directly,

00:28:42.210 --> 00:28:44.600 align:middle line:90%
but we are--

00:28:44.600 --> 00:28:46.080 align:middle line:90%
there's an order.

00:28:46.080 --> 00:28:49.200 align:middle line:84%
There's a divine
order of creation.

00:28:49.200 --> 00:28:55.190 align:middle line:84%
And the earth herself,
itself, is a god,

00:28:55.190 --> 00:28:59.310 align:middle line:84%
is a divine entity, a
powerful entity that is--

00:28:59.310 --> 00:29:00.110 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Yes.

00:29:00.110 --> 00:29:01.140 align:middle line:90%
>> IRON EYES: --very, very old.

00:29:01.140 --> 00:29:01.370 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Yes.

00:29:01.370 --> 00:29:03.690 align:middle line:84%
>> IRON EYES: Maybe 5
to 8 billion years old.

00:29:03.690 --> 00:29:05.030 align:middle line:90%
I don't even know what--

00:29:05.030 --> 00:29:07.830 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: They say even
older, I think, in the Vedas.

00:29:07.830 --> 00:29:08.720 align:middle line:90%
Yeah.

00:29:08.720 --> 00:29:10.250 align:middle line:90%
>> IRON EYES: But we also--

00:29:10.250 --> 00:29:16.970 align:middle line:84%
we have earth origins of blood
clot, simple life or organism,

00:29:16.970 --> 00:29:17.840 align:middle line:90%
what do you call it?

00:29:17.840 --> 00:29:19.760 align:middle line:90%
Maybe cellular.

00:29:19.760 --> 00:29:21.720 align:middle line:84%
We just have-- we just
call that [LAKOTA],

00:29:21.720 --> 00:29:25.200 align:middle line:84%
like the infinitesimally
small things.

00:29:25.200 --> 00:29:26.960 align:middle line:90%
But we also have--

00:29:26.960 --> 00:29:31.500 align:middle line:84%
we come through the Big
Dipper, the spirit itself.

00:29:31.500 --> 00:29:35.080 align:middle line:84%
Before you arrived
here, according to us,

00:29:35.080 --> 00:29:40.620 align:middle line:84%
you determined-- you
chose to incarnate here

00:29:40.620 --> 00:29:47.920 align:middle line:84%
and to achieve consciousness
and to be born.

00:29:47.920 --> 00:29:48.880 align:middle line:90%
You chose that.

00:29:48.880 --> 00:29:50.327 align:middle line:90%
You chose your parents.

00:29:50.327 --> 00:29:52.660 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: I'm totally on
board with what you're saying.

00:29:52.660 --> 00:29:53.130 align:middle line:90%
>> IRON EYES: And then--

00:29:53.130 --> 00:29:54.110 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: I agree.

00:29:54.110 --> 00:29:58.380 align:middle line:84%
>> IRON EYES: --when our body
expires and the divine flesh

00:29:58.380 --> 00:30:03.250 align:middle line:84%
and blood and the bones, which
the creator, you might say,

00:30:03.250 --> 00:30:07.390 align:middle line:84%
took a bit of Íŋyaŋ, the first
God, which became the stone.

00:30:07.390 --> 00:30:09.340 align:middle line:84%
And that's where
our bones come from.

00:30:09.340 --> 00:30:12.430 align:middle line:84%
The flesh and blood came
from Mother Earth herself.

00:30:12.430 --> 00:30:15.070 align:middle line:84%
So everything that is
the flesh and blood--

00:30:15.070 --> 00:30:18.520 align:middle line:84%
and then the water
is also separate.

00:30:18.520 --> 00:30:21.340 align:middle line:84%
That is a separate
god-like entity.

00:30:21.340 --> 00:30:22.860 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: I mean,
these are facts.

00:30:22.860 --> 00:30:23.040 align:middle line:90%
>> IRON EYES: They're facts.

00:30:23.040 --> 00:30:23.430 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: We are born--

00:30:23.430 --> 00:30:23.910 align:middle line:84%
>> IRON EYES:
They're scientific--

00:30:23.910 --> 00:30:24.210 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: --out
of the elements--

00:30:24.210 --> 00:30:25.060 align:middle line:90%
>> IRON EYES: --facts too.

00:30:25.060 --> 00:30:25.450 align:middle line:90%
Yes.

00:30:25.450 --> 00:30:25.650 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: --of nature.

00:30:25.650 --> 00:30:26.950 align:middle line:84%
>> IRON EYES: We
are those elements.

00:30:26.950 --> 00:30:27.780 align:middle line:90%
And so--

00:30:27.780 --> 00:30:28.905 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: No arguing that.

00:30:28.905 --> 00:30:31.290 align:middle line:84%
>> IRON EYES: But
somewhere along the way,

00:30:31.290 --> 00:30:34.500 align:middle line:84%
we got separated from
that sacred walk of life,

00:30:34.500 --> 00:30:37.400 align:middle line:90%
that sacred way of knowing.

00:30:37.400 --> 00:30:41.340 align:middle line:84%
Whatever it was stole the
sacred, stole the magic of life,

00:30:41.340 --> 00:30:47.900 align:middle line:84%
and is trying to subdue that
potential, the potential

00:30:47.900 --> 00:30:52.110 align:middle line:84%
for that heightened awareness,
that heightened consciousness.

00:30:52.110 --> 00:30:56.660 align:middle line:84%
And I even believe that the
mythology of AI and let's

00:30:56.660 --> 00:31:02.520 align:middle line:84%
go to Mars and let's colonize
Mars, we should look within.

00:31:02.520 --> 00:31:04.140 align:middle line:90%
We should look within ourselves.

00:31:04.140 --> 00:31:07.070 align:middle line:84%
We should look within
the planet herself

00:31:07.070 --> 00:31:11.660 align:middle line:84%
and figure out how to
achieve some sort of respect

00:31:11.660 --> 00:31:12.480 align:middle line:90%
relationship.

00:31:12.480 --> 00:31:15.300 align:middle line:84%
Some sort of harmony
would be great.

00:31:15.300 --> 00:31:17.780 align:middle line:90%
But it's a different world now.

00:31:17.780 --> 00:31:23.390 align:middle line:84%
We're not anti-technology, but
we are certainly pro-sacred

00:31:23.390 --> 00:31:26.270 align:middle line:84%
mythology, sacred
metaphysics, and having

00:31:26.270 --> 00:31:30.240 align:middle line:84%
all human beings be able to
have that in their lives.

00:31:30.240 --> 00:31:32.560 align:middle line:90%
And that's available to us.

00:31:32.560 --> 00:31:36.130 align:middle line:84%
But I was going to
say that the start--

00:31:36.130 --> 00:31:38.400 align:middle line:84%
when you mentioned
star people, not only

00:31:38.400 --> 00:31:40.770 align:middle line:84%
do we come from
the stars, but we

00:31:40.770 --> 00:31:46.440 align:middle line:84%
return through the same
portal that we arrived here.

00:31:46.440 --> 00:31:47.310 align:middle line:90%
And--

00:31:47.310 --> 00:31:47.700 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Big Dipper?

00:31:47.700 --> 00:31:49.450 align:middle line:84%
>> IRON EYES: Through
the Big Dipper, yes.

00:31:49.450 --> 00:31:53.132 align:middle line:84%
So maybe I don't know what our
state of knowledge is on that--

00:31:53.132 --> 00:31:54.090 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: No, that's--

00:31:54.090 --> 00:31:54.910 align:middle line:84%
>> IRON EYES:
--particular place.

00:31:54.910 --> 00:31:55.560 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: --interesting.

00:31:55.560 --> 00:31:56.360 align:middle line:90%
OK.

00:31:56.360 --> 00:32:00.430 align:middle line:84%
So now today then,
have your people

00:32:00.430 --> 00:32:03.090 align:middle line:84%
do you think-- now, we've
got to separate people

00:32:03.090 --> 00:32:05.140 align:middle line:84%
under 30 who've been
raised on devices.

00:32:05.140 --> 00:32:06.280 align:middle line:90%
It's a different world.

00:32:06.280 --> 00:32:09.180 align:middle line:84%
But generally speaking,
is there still

00:32:09.180 --> 00:32:12.188 align:middle line:84%
the sense of gratitude
toward Mother Earth?

00:32:12.188 --> 00:32:13.230 align:middle line:90%
>> IRON EYES: Absolutely.

00:32:13.230 --> 00:32:15.550 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: Because gratitude
is a very high frequency,

00:32:15.550 --> 00:32:18.660 align:middle line:84%
and I can't imagine a better
way to go into connection with

00:32:18.660 --> 00:32:20.760 align:middle line:84%
Mother Earth, which we
all have to do again.

00:32:20.760 --> 00:32:24.520 align:middle line:84%
>> IRON EYES: For us,
there's no separation.

00:32:24.520 --> 00:32:28.620 align:middle line:84%
The English language is a
tricky, little pirate commerce

00:32:28.620 --> 00:32:30.183 align:middle line:90%
slash other--

00:32:30.183 --> 00:32:31.350 align:middle line:90%
maybe other things language.

00:32:31.350 --> 00:32:35.090 align:middle line:84%
But the people who speak
Lakota, my elders--

00:32:35.090 --> 00:32:40.050 align:middle line:84%
I'm thinking of a man named Dave
Swallow who said to me, tȟókša,

00:32:40.050 --> 00:32:42.680 align:middle line:84%
it's good that you have
the-- you're a lawyer

00:32:42.680 --> 00:32:46.560 align:middle line:84%
and you got this
knowledge in that world.

00:32:46.560 --> 00:32:50.480 align:middle line:84%
But with the English
language comes doubt.

00:32:50.480 --> 00:32:52.560 align:middle line:84%
He said, with the English
language comes doubt.

00:32:52.560 --> 00:32:53.550 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Interesting.

00:32:53.550 --> 00:32:54.350 align:middle line:90%
>> IRON EYES: And--

00:32:54.350 --> 00:32:57.260 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: Is it inherent to the
English language or the mindset?

00:32:57.260 --> 00:32:57.650 align:middle line:90%
>> IRON EYES: Maybe.

00:32:57.650 --> 00:32:58.350 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Enhances it.

00:32:58.350 --> 00:32:59.150 align:middle line:90%
>> IRON EYES: Yeah.

00:32:59.150 --> 00:33:01.850 align:middle line:84%
Maybe it's just
the software itself

00:33:01.850 --> 00:33:05.840 align:middle line:84%
that's running the consciousness
allows for different things

00:33:05.840 --> 00:33:06.830 align:middle line:90%
to happen.

00:33:06.830 --> 00:33:09.063 align:middle line:84%
I don't know for
sure, but-- or he

00:33:09.063 --> 00:33:11.230 align:middle line:84%
could have just been
encouraging me to learn Lakota.

00:33:11.230 --> 00:33:14.150 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: [LAUGHS]
That's what you do.

00:33:14.150 --> 00:33:16.440 align:middle line:84%
>> IRON EYES: But we
don't see a separation.

00:33:16.440 --> 00:33:19.040 align:middle line:84%
There's a phrase we
use, [SPEAKING LAKOTA].

00:33:19.040 --> 00:33:22.680 align:middle line:90%
Everything that is my relative.

00:33:22.680 --> 00:33:27.020 align:middle line:84%
And at some point in
somewhere-- and I can only

00:33:27.020 --> 00:33:31.920 align:middle line:84%
point to maybe the
Enlightenment, or Cartesian

00:33:31.920 --> 00:33:34.870 align:middle line:84%
philosophy where there
was a separation.

00:33:34.870 --> 00:33:36.750 align:middle line:84%
The mind is separate
from the body.

00:33:36.750 --> 00:33:40.300 align:middle line:84%
Even the spirit-- they might not
even have recognized the spirit,

00:33:40.300 --> 00:33:42.100 align:middle line:84%
but the spirit was
separate from the mind.

00:33:42.100 --> 00:33:43.080 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Yes.

00:33:43.080 --> 00:33:43.500 align:middle line:90%
>> IRON EYES: The human--

00:33:43.500 --> 00:33:44.500 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: Everything
was parted out.

00:33:44.500 --> 00:33:46.600 align:middle line:84%
>> IRON EYES: Everything
got abstracted over time.

00:33:46.600 --> 00:33:48.870 align:middle line:84%
Human beings no longer
had a relationship

00:33:48.870 --> 00:33:50.580 align:middle line:90%
with their food source.

00:33:50.580 --> 00:33:52.150 align:middle line:90%
For us, it's the Buffalo.

00:33:52.150 --> 00:33:54.100 align:middle line:84%
For other cultures,
it's something else.

00:33:54.100 --> 00:34:00.060 align:middle line:84%
We no longer paid attention to
the earthly and heavenly cycles

00:34:00.060 --> 00:34:04.330 align:middle line:84%
like we once did, and
all of our ceremonies.

00:34:04.330 --> 00:34:09.960 align:middle line:84%
So we've suffered that as
well, this separation of--

00:34:09.960 --> 00:34:14.730 align:middle line:84%
this connection that we have
internally and outwardly

00:34:14.730 --> 00:34:16.900 align:middle line:90%
with the divine universe.

00:34:16.900 --> 00:34:23.460 align:middle line:84%
But our ceremonies bring
it all back into unity.

00:34:23.460 --> 00:34:28.280 align:middle line:84%
We create unitive,
transcendental experiences

00:34:28.280 --> 00:34:31.880 align:middle line:84%
through the sweat
lodge, for instance,

00:34:31.880 --> 00:34:35.150 align:middle line:84%
which combines all of
the sacred elements--

00:34:35.150 --> 00:34:41.090 align:middle line:84%
the earth, the air,
the fire, the water.

00:34:41.090 --> 00:34:42.800 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: Does
it, more or less,

00:34:42.800 --> 00:34:47.230 align:middle line:84%
then take you into an ecstatic
state of connection again with

00:34:47.230 --> 00:34:48.030 align:middle line:90%
everything?

00:34:48.030 --> 00:34:48.320 align:middle line:90%
>> IRON EYES: Yes.

00:34:48.320 --> 00:34:49.487 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: --the ceremonies?

00:34:49.487 --> 00:34:51.170 align:middle line:90%
>> IRON EYES: It provides a--

00:34:51.170 --> 00:34:54.090 align:middle line:90%
it's a portal and a womb to us.

00:34:54.090 --> 00:34:57.330 align:middle line:90%
And it's our oldest ceremony.

00:34:57.330 --> 00:35:00.150 align:middle line:84%
And it's the one that
is most widespread.

00:35:00.150 --> 00:35:03.630 align:middle line:90%
The Lakota people are sharers.

00:35:03.630 --> 00:35:08.310 align:middle line:84%
I like to say we're small, but
we're global in our approach.

00:35:08.310 --> 00:35:09.620 align:middle line:90%
Some people are not.

00:35:09.620 --> 00:35:12.900 align:middle line:84%
Some people are like,
no, let's not do that.

00:35:12.900 --> 00:35:15.110 align:middle line:84%
Let's pull you
back a little bit.

00:35:15.110 --> 00:35:16.680 align:middle line:90%
And I respect that.

00:35:16.680 --> 00:35:17.540 align:middle line:90%
But I was just--

00:35:17.540 --> 00:35:20.420 align:middle line:84%
I have teachers like
chief Leonard Crow

00:35:20.420 --> 00:35:21.700 align:middle line:90%
Dog, who's no longer with us--

00:35:21.700 --> 00:35:22.500 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Yes.

00:35:22.500 --> 00:35:23.285 align:middle line:84%
>> IRON EYES: But
he was-- it was--

00:35:23.285 --> 00:35:23.390 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Wounded Knee.

00:35:23.390 --> 00:35:25.390 align:middle line:84%
>> IRON EYES: --because
of people like him, yes,

00:35:25.390 --> 00:35:29.640 align:middle line:84%
that the sweat lodge ceremony,
the sundance ceremony has gained

00:35:29.640 --> 00:35:37.440 align:middle line:84%
at least a Western Hemispheric
presence and respect and created

00:35:37.440 --> 00:35:39.610 align:middle line:90%
allies of the Lakota people.

00:35:39.610 --> 00:35:40.840 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: That is true.

00:35:40.840 --> 00:35:47.190 align:middle line:84%
But I also wonder how you feel
about essentially the white man

00:35:47.190 --> 00:35:48.790 align:middle line:90%
also co-opting--

00:35:48.790 --> 00:35:50.980 align:middle line:84%
>> IRON EYES: Oh,
that's a problem.

00:35:50.980 --> 00:35:51.780 align:middle line:90%
That--

00:35:51.780 --> 00:35:53.980 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: It seems like
it would be a problem--

00:35:53.980 --> 00:35:55.542 align:middle line:84%
it seems like it
would be a problem.

00:35:55.542 --> 00:35:57.250 align:middle line:84%
>> IRON EYES: It's
definitely a problem--

00:35:57.250 --> 00:35:59.670 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: I can't tell you
how many white Native American

00:35:59.670 --> 00:36:02.080 align:middle line:90%
shamans want to be interviewed.

00:36:02.080 --> 00:36:05.110 align:middle line:84%
>> IRON EYES:
They're seeking too.

00:36:05.110 --> 00:36:06.520 align:middle line:90%
They're seeking a connection.

00:36:06.520 --> 00:36:09.020 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: I know that, and
there's nothing wrong with that.

00:36:09.020 --> 00:36:12.302 align:middle line:84%
But from your point of view,
it seems like co-opting to me.

00:36:12.302 --> 00:36:13.510 align:middle line:90%
>> IRON EYES: It's co-opting.

00:36:13.510 --> 00:36:18.420 align:middle line:84%
And they don't know a
whole lot, and there's

00:36:18.420 --> 00:36:21.900 align:middle line:84%
a concept called
[LAKOTA] in our language,

00:36:21.900 --> 00:36:26.180 align:middle line:84%
which means having a
humility about things,

00:36:26.180 --> 00:36:30.050 align:middle line:84%
like an innate experience
or innate respect.

00:36:30.050 --> 00:36:33.350 align:middle line:84%
There's just certain things
that we wouldn't do--

00:36:33.350 --> 00:36:36.350 align:middle line:84%
we wouldn't mess around
with certain things,

00:36:36.350 --> 00:36:38.570 align:middle line:84%
because we respect
them too much,

00:36:38.570 --> 00:36:41.220 align:middle line:84%
and they're going to have
real-life consequences.

00:36:41.220 --> 00:36:44.250 align:middle line:84%
Benefits, blessings,
consequences.

00:36:44.250 --> 00:36:47.120 align:middle line:90%
All of that comes from--

00:36:47.120 --> 00:36:50.340 align:middle line:84%
it's seeking out
that connection.

00:36:50.340 --> 00:36:54.480 align:middle line:84%
It takes a person to
take that step forward.

00:36:54.480 --> 00:36:57.120 align:middle line:84%
If you want to know
more, then, hey,

00:36:57.120 --> 00:36:59.150 align:middle line:84%
you're going to have to
go into a sweat lodge

00:36:59.150 --> 00:37:00.725 align:middle line:90%
and purify yourself.

00:37:00.725 --> 00:37:02.100 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: So
let's look at that.

00:37:02.100 --> 00:37:03.930 align:middle line:84%
So people listening
are thinking,

00:37:03.930 --> 00:37:07.140 align:middle line:84%
oh my god, my soul, I can
feel I need this purification.

00:37:07.140 --> 00:37:08.940 align:middle line:84%
I need this connection
with nature.

00:37:08.940 --> 00:37:10.700 align:middle line:90%
And what a beautiful language.

00:37:10.700 --> 00:37:13.950 align:middle line:84%
And getting some
kind of desire--

00:37:13.950 --> 00:37:14.750 align:middle line:90%
>> IRON EYES: Yes.

00:37:14.750 --> 00:37:15.708 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: --worked up.

00:37:15.708 --> 00:37:16.970 align:middle line:90%
And how do they do that?

00:37:16.970 --> 00:37:18.470 align:middle line:84%
Because a lot of
your ceremonies are

00:37:18.470 --> 00:37:20.280 align:middle line:84%
closed and they're
for your people.

00:37:20.280 --> 00:37:21.710 align:middle line:90%
>> IRON EYES: Yeah.

00:37:21.710 --> 00:37:26.130 align:middle line:84%
There's a lot of-- a lot of
our people have already--

00:37:26.130 --> 00:37:29.560 align:middle line:84%
they've already done what
I'm doing right now with you,

00:37:29.560 --> 00:37:34.060 align:middle line:84%
which is exploring in a
very respectful, potent way

00:37:34.060 --> 00:37:37.560 align:middle line:84%
the depths and the
sources of what we are

00:37:37.560 --> 00:37:38.980 align:middle line:90%
and how we're connected.

00:37:38.980 --> 00:37:41.800 align:middle line:90%
I can-- John Fire Lame Deer.

00:37:41.800 --> 00:37:44.430 align:middle line:84%
Chief Leonard Crow Dog,
there's a less known--

00:37:44.430 --> 00:37:47.490 align:middle line:84%
he wouldn't write a book,
but he was my first teacher.

00:37:47.490 --> 00:37:50.670 align:middle line:84%
His name is Sunny
Richards, and I could not

00:37:50.670 --> 00:37:52.030 align:middle line:90%
get him to write a book.

00:37:52.030 --> 00:37:54.400 align:middle line:84%
But he said, if there's a
book that could be written,

00:37:54.400 --> 00:37:59.700 align:middle line:84%
it's about the dark arts
and how human beings

00:37:59.700 --> 00:38:01.500 align:middle line:90%
are susceptible to--

00:38:01.500 --> 00:38:02.880 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Oh, boy, yes.

00:38:02.880 --> 00:38:03.990 align:middle line:90%
The manipulation of--

00:38:03.990 --> 00:38:04.880 align:middle line:84%
>> IRON EYES: That
negative source of it.

00:38:04.880 --> 00:38:06.797 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: Oh, we're
watching it all play out.

00:38:06.797 --> 00:38:10.990 align:middle line:84%
>> IRON EYES: And human beings--
we're only human beings.

00:38:10.990 --> 00:38:14.520 align:middle line:84%
So we try to be good, and
we try to redeem ourselves,

00:38:14.520 --> 00:38:17.020 align:middle line:90%
and we try to walk in that way.

00:38:17.020 --> 00:38:17.820 align:middle line:90%
But--

00:38:17.820 --> 00:38:19.153 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: But we're vulnerable.

00:38:19.153 --> 00:38:20.440 align:middle line:90%
We're credulous people.

00:38:20.440 --> 00:38:21.435 align:middle line:90%
We're human.

00:38:21.435 --> 00:38:22.235 align:middle line:90%
We're credulous.

00:38:22.235 --> 00:38:23.035 align:middle line:90%
>> IRON EYES: Yes.

00:38:23.035 --> 00:38:26.300 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: We tend to absorb
what we're exposed to, and a lot

00:38:26.300 --> 00:38:28.880 align:middle line:84%
of it is driven by
trauma and fear, sadly,

00:38:28.880 --> 00:38:31.338 align:middle line:84%
which once you're in trauma,
you'll believe anything pretty

00:38:31.338 --> 00:38:32.138 align:middle line:90%
much.

00:38:32.138 --> 00:38:33.030 align:middle line:90%
You're wide open.

00:38:33.030 --> 00:38:35.330 align:middle line:84%
So learning without
trauma and fear

00:38:35.330 --> 00:38:38.390 align:middle line:84%
more along the lines of
appreciation, gratitude.

00:38:38.390 --> 00:38:41.165 align:middle line:84%
Like you're talking about
being in unity or harmony.

00:38:41.165 --> 00:38:43.290 align:middle line:84%
>> IRON EYES: You may have
heard of like Black Elk.

00:38:43.290 --> 00:38:44.258 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Yes.

00:38:44.258 --> 00:38:46.050 align:middle line:84%
>> IRON EYES: He became
Nicholas Black Elk.

00:38:46.050 --> 00:38:48.840 align:middle line:90%
He might become a Saint.

00:38:48.840 --> 00:38:50.910 align:middle line:90%
He's nominated for sainthood--

00:38:50.910 --> 00:38:51.920 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Oh, lovely.

00:38:51.920 --> 00:38:53.780 align:middle line:90%
>> IRON EYES: Yes.

00:38:53.780 --> 00:38:57.950 align:middle line:84%
But like, we know the
descendants of Mr.--

00:38:57.950 --> 00:38:59.860 align:middle line:90%
Black's Elk is a--

00:38:59.860 --> 00:39:03.210 align:middle line:84%
the fact that he hooked up with
a non-native guy, a white guy,

00:39:03.210 --> 00:39:06.290 align:middle line:84%
a European guy, John
G. Neihardt, and they

00:39:06.290 --> 00:39:07.980 align:middle line:90%
wrote Black Elk Speaks.

00:39:07.980 --> 00:39:11.330 align:middle line:84%
They wrote other things too,
but that was the first book

00:39:11.330 --> 00:39:16.320 align:middle line:84%
that I read that
sent me on a journey.

00:39:16.320 --> 00:39:20.730 align:middle line:84%
I was raised not in any way
as a-- in a Christian way,

00:39:20.730 --> 00:39:22.140 align:middle line:90%
but a lot of Native people are.

00:39:22.140 --> 00:39:23.980 align:middle line:84%
I'm not trying to say
anything about that.

00:39:23.980 --> 00:39:27.321 align:middle line:84%
I'm saying that my mom
took me to Native ceremony.

00:39:27.321 --> 00:39:28.196 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Wonderful.

00:39:28.196 --> 00:39:30.180 align:middle line:90%
>> IRON EYES: [SPEAKING LAKOTA].

00:39:30.180 --> 00:39:33.250 align:middle line:84%
We would go-- she would
take me to the ceremonies.

00:39:33.250 --> 00:39:35.500 align:middle line:84%
And I remember the
ceremonies as a kid.

00:39:35.500 --> 00:39:37.240 align:middle line:84%
I didn't understand
what was going on,

00:39:37.240 --> 00:39:39.570 align:middle line:84%
but I remember
being there, and I

00:39:39.570 --> 00:39:43.410 align:middle line:84%
remember having divine
experiences, you might say,

00:39:43.410 --> 00:39:48.990 align:middle line:84%
things that challenge the
laws of physics or somebody's

00:39:48.990 --> 00:39:51.580 align:middle line:84%
understanding of
how reality works.

00:39:51.580 --> 00:39:55.470 align:middle line:84%
It's all fluid, and
it's all up for--

00:39:55.470 --> 00:39:58.860 align:middle line:90%
