00:39:58.860 --> 00:40:01.510 align:middle line:84%
Yes, you can trust your
senses for a lot of things,

00:40:01.510 --> 00:40:04.080 align:middle line:84%
but you should also
be aware that there

00:40:04.080 --> 00:40:07.680 align:middle line:84%
are other potentialities
that are there.

00:40:07.680 --> 00:40:12.330 align:middle line:84%
That are there for us to
access, for us to heal.

00:40:12.330 --> 00:40:16.510 align:middle line:84%
And so from Black Elk's
time to, I would say--

00:40:16.510 --> 00:40:20.610 align:middle line:84%
