interface-- he's

00:40:29.500 --> 00:40:32.240 align:middle line:84%
trying to treat tuberculosis,
an outbreak of that.

00:40:32.240 --> 00:40:36.060 align:middle line:84%
So he says, I can't handle
this in my own Western medical

00:40:36.060 --> 00:40:36.860 align:middle line:90%
training.

00:40:36.860 --> 00:40:40.280 align:middle line:84%
I need the help of these
shaman, of these [LAKOTA],

00:40:40.280 --> 00:40:42.050 align:middle line:90%
these intercessors.

00:40:42.050 --> 00:40:46.420 align:middle line:84%
And so he obtains the help of
people like American Horse, who

00:40:46.420 --> 00:40:51.310 align:middle line:84%
