people like Rick Two Dogs,

00:40:51.310 --> 00:40:54.400 align:middle line:90%
who Rick doesn't do a lot of--

00:40:54.400 --> 00:40:56.080 align:middle line:90%
these are guys--

00:40:56.080 --> 00:41:01.000 align:middle line:84%
Rick Two Dogs and Dickey
Moves Camp are probably the--

00:41:01.000 --> 00:41:05.800 align:middle line:84%
those two plus Crow Dog were
like the most well respected

00:41:05.800 --> 00:41:08.440 align:middle line:90%
spiritual people of our nation.

00:41:08.440 --> 00:41:13.280 align:middle line:84%
And Dickey Moves Camp,
we've talked to him.

00:41:13.280 --> 00:41:15.170 align:middle line:90%
