00:42:18.310 --> 00:42:23.830 align:middle line:84%
We have religions,
you might say,

00:42:23.830 --> 00:42:26.770 align:middle line:84%
we have cultural
knowledge that connects us

00:42:26.770 --> 00:42:32.200 align:middle line:84%
