00:42:35.230 --> 00:42:39.580 align:middle line:84%
and all the other gods in our
way of knowing that there's

00:42:39.580 --> 00:42:42.730 align:middle line:90%
16 gods, you might say.

00:42:42.730 --> 00:42:46.610 align:middle line:84%
And there's an order
for those 16 gods.

00:42:46.610 --> 00:42:54.160 align:middle line:84%
Our ceremonies, the way
that our mythology instills

00:42:54.160 --> 00:42:57.640 align:middle line:84%
in us this innate
relationship, but more--

00:42:57.640 --> 00:43:05.680 align:middle line:84%
beyond that, a covenant to
defend the rights of those

00:43:05.680 --> 00:43:11.530 align:middle line:84%
nonhuman entities that are here
that predated the two-legged

00:43:11.530 --> 00:43:12.330 align:middle line:90%
being here--

00:43:12.330 --> 00:43:13.330 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Our teachers.

00:43:13.330 --> 00:43:15.080 align:middle line:84%
>> IRON EYES: --from
which we derive--

00:43:15.080 --> 00:43:18.280 align:middle line:84%
from which we derive
our spiritual authority

00:43:18.280 --> 00:43:22.420 align:middle line:84%
